# Prevent Cursor Agent from breaking server-side code
protect:
  - "src/lib/supabase/**"
  - "src/lib/db/tasks.ts"
  - "src/app/**/actions.ts"
  - "supabase/**"

# Keep server actions intact
rule: Preserve all `"use server"` blocks, server action functions, and Supabase calls.
rule: Do not rename or remove input `name` attributes (these bind to server actions).

# Scope
rule: Default to UI-only changes: Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui components, layout, validation, accessibility.
rule: Do not add dependencies without explicit approval.
rule: Fix any TypeScript errors you introduce, without disabling type-checks.
